description.en:
An Autonomous Yield and deflationary token model. This deflationary model works on scarcity. The more transactions that take place the more tokens will keep decreasing from the total supply along every trade contributes toward automatically generating locked locked liquidity. With higher demand and less supply $TORPEDO holders will ultimately be rewarded with a higher price!

5% fee redistributed to all existing holders. 5% fee is been added as a locked liquidity to create higher price floor.
